
Project Step 6

USE CASE: Basketball

Actors
customer

Trigger
customer indicates they want to sign up to play basketball

Precondition
there must be a form to sign up to play

Post-condition
customer will be signed up to play

Normal Flow

The user will make an account if they don't have one
The user will log in
The user selects an team and indicates they would like to play
The user will be presented with an sign up form to fill out
The user will submit the form
The system will prompt the user to confirm all information is correct
The system will send a conformation email to customer
The user will exit the system

Alternate Flow
A. The user will discover the team they selected is unavailable.
The system will prompt an error that the team they selected is unavailable.
The use case returns to step 4
